title: Moroccan grilled salmon
ingredients: ['1 small bunch fresh coriander', '1 small bunch flat-leaf parsley', '80ml olive oil', '1 to 2 garlic cloves', '1 teaspoon white wine vinegar', '1 teaspoon lemon juice', '1/2 teaspoon ground paprika', '1/2 teaspoon ground cumin', '1 generous pinch of cayenne pepper', 'salt and black pepper to taste', '2 salmon fillets without skin']
